Table 3: Results of framework in Re-ID. ResNet + S-Reid stands for Saliency subnet using ResNet as backbone. Analogously, SP-ReID refers 
to Semantic Parsing subnet, whereas SSP-ReID refers to the complete framework. We highlight in red color the cases in which the subnet-
work/framework is worse than the original backbone, whereas cases with better results than backbone are highlighted in blue color.
